*pyside-1.0.0 (20 Mar 2011)

  20 Mar 2011; Tomas Touceda <chiiph@gentoo.org> +pyside-1.0.0.ebuild:
  Version bump

  29 Dec 2010; Dominik Kapusta <ayoy@gentoo.org> pyside-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Specifying correct dependency on Python (bug #345531).

  23 Dec 2010; Dominik Kapusta <ayoy@gentoo.org> pyside-0.4.2.ebuild,
  +files/pyside-cmake-namespace.patch:
  Add patch to fix namespace issue in cmake files (bug #348632). Thanks to
  tarek for the patch.

*pyside-0.4.2 (25 Nov 2010)

  25 Nov 2010; Tomas Touceda <chiiph@gentoo.org> -pyside-0.3.2.ebuild,
  -pyside-0.4.0-r1.ebuild, +pyside-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Version bump, remove old and restrict tests wrt bug 338485

*pyside-0.4.0-r1 (25 Aug 2010)

